entries.title_d: Remain in the Dantooine system and inspect the Velocity mercenary captain. The officer's starfighter has been spotted on your radar. Intercept, disable, and inspect that vessel.
entries.title: Dantooine System: Inspect the Velocity Mercenary Captain
entries.split_quest_alert: Interesting, the reports you have recovered have a communications relay point and frequency indicated in them. Travel to location and tune into the frequency.
entries.quest_location_d: The target vessels signal is coming from inside the Dantooine system. Intercept the Velocity mercenary captain at the supplied navigation waypoint.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Disable and inspect the captain for any information regarding their operation in the Dantooine system.
entries.quest_dock_d: Once you have found the navigation charts, dock with the vessel and transfer the charts to your ship.
